# Settings and Template Sync

- Selected print template must be a single global state.
- Dashboard, PrintView, TemplatesView, and Settings must stay synchronized.
- Do not use hardcoded or mock template lists in views.
- Template ComboBox, selected cards, summaries, and previews must use the same source.
- Settings changes must refresh all connected views without requiring app restart.
- Persist selected template through settings and validate that it still exists in the shared template list.
- Prefer `PrintTemplateService` plus shared MainWindow/UI state over local copies in individual views.
